window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cole Winchester loves being one of the most popular bachelors in New York. He values his freedom and all the perks it comes with.</p> <p>But when he notices Laney Smith at the restaurant where he’s celebrating his most recent business deal, he can’t look away. Everything from her curves to her humor and easy smile completely captivates him.</p> <p>Laney’s sole focus for the past few years has been her surgical residency. Her work is her passion and her refuge. Laney has loved and lost, and she can’t open up again, despite trying her best.</p> <p>But Cole is hellbent on changing that. He’s melting her fears with every kiss and touch. This determined charmer is ready to move mountains to make her happy and help her heal.</p> <p>And she might just let him.</p>"; 
